# Assets Exposures Leases Amount

## identifier
de7989

## type
float

## definition
This is the value of all exposures (both on and off balance sheet) arising from finance leases receivable by the reporting party as at the relevant date.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Assets.ExposuresLeases.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo1.02.06
- period=instant
